title: TOP 100 R&B SONGS (1990-2008)
description:
As promised, I am back with my new compilation: TOP 100 R&B SONGS.  Here is my list of the Top 100 R&B songs made between approx 1990 - 2008.  This is my best work to date!  There aren't any top 100 R&B lists anywhere with a collection of great R&B songs like these, and what compilation lists I have found have crappy ass songs by artists like Da Brat or En Vogue or something.

This is my 3rd list of the TOP 100 lists of all my different genres of music, and I'll have the rest posted shortly.  If you would like to see the other entitled:

This list is unique because it includes lots of old school songs by R. Kelly and Nate Dogg, but it also has lots of new R&B tracks from Craig David and Avant and so forth.  In addition, it has tracks like "Ride Wit U" and "Smile" by G-Unit and "Karma" by Lloyd Banks that are great R&B songs but aren't often grouped in R&B compilations b/c they're made by rappers.

Feel free to leave comments for me below.  Both of my previous torrents have been very popular, so I'm hoping this one will be as well.  Both the song list below and the file list is listed in alphabetical order by song title for easy cross-reference (if you only want to download a few songs).  1 or 2 of the songs are in wma format, but iTunes will automatically convert them (sorry).
